OL,4,CChina steps in to regulate brutal '996'
OL,5,Cwork culture
OL,6, Chinese tech tycoon Jack Ma famously
OL,7, said it was a "blessing" for anyone to
OL,8, be part of the so-called "996 work
OL,9, culture"- where people work 9am to 9pm,
OL,10, six days a week.
OL,12,FNow, China's authorities have issued a
OL,13,Fstern reminder to companies that such
OL,14,Fpunishing work schedules are in fact,
OL,15,Fillegal.
OL,18,FThe cases covered various scenarios
OL,19,Facross a wide range of sectors, from
OL,20,Ftech to the media and construction.
